{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotations:"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotations:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotations"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"array must conform to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations in the array."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotations:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind